methods.doRehash:
:param fullRehash: (boolean) - should we rehash the entire table (if false, we rehash incrementally)
:param rehashCredits: (org.apache.commons.lang3.mutable.MutableInt) - the number of rehash buckets this operation has rehashed (input/output)
:param nextChunkSize: (int) - the size of the chunk we are processing, we need to make at least twice as many rehash
        credits available
:return: (boolean) true if a front migration is required
